    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3>SubBreeds table</h3>
<p>The SubBreeds table contains the specific sub-breeds associated with each dog breed, including the name of the sub-breed and a reference to its parent breed.</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Column Name</th>
      <th>Type</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>id</td>
      <td>Integer</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>name</td>
      <td>String</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>breed_id</td>
      <td>Integer (Foreign Key)</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

